   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00005"/>Herrn <hi rend="latintype">Dr Richard Beer-Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#pmb173" type="place"><hi rend="latintype">Rodaun</hi></rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs ref="#pmb40101" type="place">Liesinger Straße 2</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00007"/><date when="1904-04-26">Din<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>tg, 26. 4. 904</date></dateline></opener><p><salute>lieber Richard,</salute> aus einer <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01395-1"/>Karte <rs type="person" ref="#pmb11740">Hugos</rs><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01395-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L01394"/>.
               </note> vom <rs type="place" ref="#pmb189">Semmering</rs> entnehme ich da<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s er
               die meine nicht erhalten hat. Die<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e meine Karte<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chlug ein Rendezvous für <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01395-2"/><date>Mittwoch Abend</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01395-2"><ref target="1904-04-27" subtype="See" type="schnitzler-tagebuch"/>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs type="place" ref="#pmb304">Hietzing <hi rend="latintype">Kuffner</hi></rs> vor und bat ihn, das <pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00008"/>auch Ihnen mitzutheilen.
               Es wär mir, <hi rend="latintype">resp</hi> uns beiden <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2173">Olga</rs> u mir<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehr lieb, Sie Beide noch vor un<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>erer Abrei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e zu<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ehen. <subst><del rend="overwritten"><unclear>Jed</unclear></del><add place="inline">W</add></subst>ir werden al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o jedenfalls in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb63">Hietzing</rs><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>ein. (Auch <rs type="person" ref="#pmb10815">Bahr</rs> hatt’ ich ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chrieben.)</p><closer><pb facs="1904_AS_RBH_1_00008"/>Herzlich<lb/>Ihr<lb/><signed>Arthur</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
